樣樣都take it for granted <br />\n一係死忍 一係果斷離場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所以咪搞到所有嘢都放係心到算<br />\n等自己慢慢釋懷<br />\n反正都冇人想聽我講<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0838a6df82d533851c30b1dc3203de94abd8b385","tid":43881,"uid":51515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T20:05:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真好笑 我只係用番你地對我嘅方式對番你地<br />\n點解可以話番我轉頭</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n人係咁架啦 樣樣都take it for granted <br />\n一係死忍 一係果斷離場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所以咪搞到所有嘢都放係心到算<br />\n等自己慢慢釋懷<br />\n反正都冇人想聽我講<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有呀 唔介意嘅咪講黎聽下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時真係唔好忍住忍住 容量有限架咋 死忍爛忍到忍唔住個日都係出事"},{"pid":"de13dccc44565eaaa84c88fbf856eea763802798","tid":43881,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T20:06:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44bd8afc2fb7073b002f91bfb3815209c255e23e","tid":43881,"uid":23901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T20:08:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁咪清一清佢 重新黎過囉 再唔係咪買過個新hard disc 舊呢一個咪放埋一邊先囉</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n原因係執著？特別係身邊人既煩惱 每日都見到 真係放唔低 總會覺得佢地覺得所有野都係我問題咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n部分係啦 點會所有野都關你事呀 每個都有煩惱 巴打點可以攬晒上身架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都唔想 某程度上我覺得因為我形象比較無所謂<br />\n令到身邊人永遠都覺得係我問題而其他人無問題"},{"pid":"d3efa82c070690bfdd20fc829ebfa86627e35548","tid":43881,"uid":36909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T20:10:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都好想喊 但十幾年無喊喇 我懷疑自己已經唔識喊<br />\n但個心一直頂住頂住真係好辛苦 想訓都訓唔到<br />\n其實係咪我太著緊？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n